Seems like the logback-elasticsearch-appender is no longer maintained and that the properties for elastic using the &lt; property &gt; is reserved.
Fixed by using fork https://github.com/agido-malter/logback-elasticsearch-appender

updated following:

    &lt;springProfile name=&quot;${KIBANA_LOGGING_PROFILE_NAME}&quot;&gt;
        &lt;appender name=&quot;ElasticSearch&quot;
            class=&quot;com.agido.logback.elasticsearch.ElasticsearchAppender&quot;&gt;
            &lt;url&gt;${ELASTIC_SEARCH_SERVER_URL}/_bulk&lt;/url&gt;
            &lt;index&gt;logs-%date{yyyy-MM-dd}&lt;/index&gt;
            &lt;type&gt;tester&lt;/type&gt;
            &lt;loggerName&gt;elastic-search-logger&lt;/loggerName&gt;
            &lt;errorLoggerName&gt;elastic-search-error-logger
            &lt;/errorLoggerName&gt;
            &lt;connectTimeout&gt;30000&lt;/connectTimeout&gt;
            &lt;errorsToStderr&gt;false&lt;/errorsToStderr&gt;
            &lt;includeCallerData&gt;false&lt;/includeCallerData&gt;
            &lt;logsToStderr&gt;false&lt;/logsToStderr&gt;
